title: What Else is Going to Come Out # 999 (Ep 999)
description:
In this episode I address the Democrats’ complete face-plant on Capitol Hill yesterday. I also address a disastrous new healthcare policy in California. Finally, I address a series of explosive new emails that expose the depths of the Spygate scandal. 

News Picks:The State Department has some serious explaining to do. 

John Solomon’s piece lays out the relationship between key Spygate figures and APCO.

The Democrats’ John Dean hearing blew up in their faces yesterday.

Christopher Steele’s suspicious ties to the State Department are being exposed.

The investigation into the Spygate scandal is expanding.
